column2: §MED-P: Default Prison: House Arrest§!
Set a policy for the default location in which prisoners will be held: §Yhouse arrest§!.
§MED-P: Default Prison: Dungeon§!
Set a policy for the default location in which prisoners will be held: §Ythe dungeon§!.
§MED-P: Default Prison: Oubliette§!
Set a policy for the default location in which prisoners will be held: §Ythe oubliette§!.
§MED-P: Move All Prisoners: House Arrest§!

Relocate §YALL§! of §Y[Root.GetTitledFirstName]§!'s prisoners to §Yhouse arrest§!.\n-\n(Unlike the "§MED-P: Move Prisoners§!" decisions, this does not differentiate by the prisoner's originating court.)
§MED-P: Move All Prisoners: Dungeon§!

Relocate §YALL§! of §Y[Root.GetTitledFirstName]§!'s prisoners to §Ythe dungeon§!\n-\n(Unlike the "§MED-P: Move Prisoners§!" decisions, this does not differentiate by the prisoner's originating court.)
§MED-P: Move All Prisoners: Oubliette§!

Relocate §YALL§! of §Y[Root.GetTitledFirstName]§!'s prisoners to §Ythe oubliette§!\n-\n(Unlike the "§MED-P: Move Prisoners§!" decisions, this does not differentiate by the prisoner's originating court.)
§Y[Root.GetTitledFirstName]§! is not already sending prisoners to §Yhouse arrest§! by default
§Y[Root.GetTitledFirstName]§! is not already sending prisoners to §Ythe dungeon§! by default
§Y[Root.GetTitledFirstName]§! is not already sending prisoners to §Ythe oubliette§! by default
All new prisoners will be sent to §Yhouse arrest§! by default
All new prisoners will be sent to §Ythe dungeon§! by default
All new prisoners will be sent to §Ythe oubliette§! by default
All current prisoners will be moved to §Yhouse arrest§!
All current prisoners will be moved to §Ythe dungeon§!
All current prisoners will be moved to §Ythe oubliette§!
§Y[Root.GetTitledFirstName]§! has at least one prisoner NOT in §Yhouse arrest§!
§Y[Root.GetTitledFirstName]§! has at least one prisoner NOT in §Ythe dungeon§!
§Y[Root.GetTitledFirstName]§! has at least one prisoner NOT in §Ythe oubliette§!
Moved to §Yhouse arrest§!
Moved to §Ythe dungeon§!
Moved to §Ythe oubliette§!
